<div class="homepage-container container">
    <div class="row welcome">
        <h2>Welcome to Locked In!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="container text-center">
            {{#if logged_in}}
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="row">
                            {{!-- New bet button --}}
                            <button type="button" class="button-card" id="new-bet-button">Make a Bet Now!</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{else}}
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                {{!-- New bet button --}}
                                <button type="button" class="button-card" id="new-bet-button">Make a Bet Now!</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-1">
                        <div class="card" id="or">OR</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                {{!-- Login button --}}
                                <button type="button" class="button-card" id="login-button">Log In</button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                {{!-- Signup button --}}
                                <button type="button" class="button-card" id="signup-button">Sign Up</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        {{!--  --}}
        <div class="col-md-7 container">
            <div class="card left-bar">
                <h2 class="card-header">How to Play</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Welcome to Locked In, the app that lets you make casual bets with your friends!</p>
                    <p>To use Locked In, sign up for a free account by clicking on the Login button. Once you have an account, you can go to your Profile page to propose a bet to a friend. If they accept, the bet is on!</p>
                    <p>Once you have decided the bet, you and your friend both vote on who won the bet. If you both agree, the winner of the bet is recorded, otherwise it counts as a tie.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card left-bar">
                <h2 class="card-header">Stats</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3>Total Bets to Date</h3>
                    <p>So far, {{stats.num_bets}} bets have been made with Locked In. Will you make the next one?</p>
                    <h3>Biggest Win</h3>
                    <p>The biggest win to date is ${{stats.big_win}}. Nice!</p>
                    <h3>Biggest Loss</h3>
                    <p>The biggest loss to date is ${{stats.big_loss}}. Bummer!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{!-- Sidebar --}}
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="card right-bar">
                <h2 class="card-header">Recent Bets</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        {{#each bets as |bet|}}
                        <a href="/bet/{{bet.id}}">
                            <li class="list-group-item">
                                <h3>{{bet.winner.username}} won ${{bet.amount}}</h3>
                                {{#each bet.users as |user|}}
                                <p>{{user.username}} bet ${{user.stake.amount}}</p>
                                {{/each}}
                            </li>
                        </a>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tutorial-container">
        <h3>GETTING STARTED</h3>
        <div class="make-bet">
            <div class="make-bet-text">
                <h4>LOGGIN AND MAKE A NEW BET</h4>
                <p>Or sign up if you haven't already</p>
                <p>Making a new bet requires the opposing username, a title for the bet, and the stake amount</p>
            </div>
            <div class="make-bet-video">
                <video src="/videos/making-a-bet.mp4" autoplay loop muted></video>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accepting-bet">
            <div class="accept-bet-video">
                <video src="/videos/accept-bet.mp4" autoplay loop muted></video>
            </div>
            <div class="accept-bet-text">
                <h4>ACCEPT INCOMING BETS</h4>
                <p>Any bets that someone has sent you are able to be accepted or denied</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="make-bet">
            <div class="make-bet-text">
                <h4>VOTE ON THE WINNER</h4>
                <p>After deciding who won the challenge, you are able to vote on the winner</p>
                <p>If votes are not unanimous, then the bet will be voided</p>
            </div>
            <div class="make-bet-video" id="vote-video">
                <video src="/videos/voting.mp4" autoplay loop muted></video>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    {{!-- New bet button --}}
                    <button type="button" class="button-card" id="new-bet-button">Make a Bet Now!</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{{#unless logged_in}}
    <script src="js/homepageBtns.js"></script>
{{/unless}}

<script src="/js/homepage.js"></script>